CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Silynx designs and builds best-in-class, ruggedized headset systems that seamlessly integrate with professional radios and personal protective gear to ensure clear communications while also protecting the hearing of elite warfighters, law enforcement, shooting enthusiasts, and industrial professionals. Exceptional, sleek in-ear systems and classic over-the-ear models enhance the efforts of tactical and industrial teams and help them prevail. Premium components and best-in-class engineering are vital for those who go in harm's way. Trusted and rugged like the teams they support.
